p class=\"entry-title\"><strong style=\"font-size: 17px\">Na inrestsro.sk pou\u017e\u00edvame cookies pre zabezpe\u010denie \u010do najlep\u0161ieho z\u00e1\u017eitku na na\u0161ej webovej str\u00e1nke.<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/header>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Pod\u013ea legislat\u00edvy EU sme povinn\u00ed V\u00e1s informova\u0165 o pou\u017eit\u00ed t\u00fdchto Cookies na\u0161ou str\u00e1nkou a slu\u017ebami tret\u00edch str\u00e1n.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=&#8221;row&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; background_size=&#8221;initial&#8221; background_position=&#8221;top_left&#8221; background_repeat=&#8221;repeat&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; custom_padding__hover=&#8221;|||&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; background_size=&#8221;initial&#8221; background_position=&#8221;top_left&#8221; background_repeat=&#8221;repeat&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2>\u010co je cookie?<\/h2>\n<p>Cookie je mal\u00fd textov\u00fd s\u00fabor. Ke\u010f si prehliadate webov\u00fa str\u00e1nku, str\u00e1nka si uklad\u00e1 tento s\u00fabor do vyhraden\u00e9ho miesta pre Cookies na Va\u0161om po\u010d\u00edta\u010di alebo mobilnom zariaden\u00ed. Pou\u017eit\u00edm Cookies webstr\u00e1nka uklad\u00e1\u00a0na ur\u010dit\u00fd \u010das inform\u00e1cie o Va\u0161ich preferovan\u00fdch nastaveniach alebo aktivit\u00e1ch, ako napr\u00edklad login, jazyk, ve\u013ekos\u0165 p\u00edsma, obsah ko\u0161\u00edka a in\u00e9. Nabud\u00face ke\u010f nav\u0161t\u00edvite str\u00e1nku ich nemus\u00edte v\u010faka cookies nastavova\u0165 odznova.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=&#8221;row&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; background_size=&#8221;initial&#8221; background_position=&#8221;top_left&#8221; background_repeat=&#8221;repeat&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; custom_padding__hover=&#8221;|||&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; background_size=&#8221;initial&#8221; background_position=&#8221;top_left&#8221; background_repeat=&#8221;repeat&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2>Ako pou\u017e\u00edvame cookies<strong>?<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pou\u017e\u00edvame Google Analytics softv\u00e9r pre zber inform\u00e1ci\u00ed o tom ako pou\u017e\u00edvate na\u0161u str\u00e1nku. Rob\u00edme to pre zlep\u0161enie na\u0161ich slu\u017eieb a za \u00fa\u010delom monitorovania v\u00fdkonu na\u0161ej str\u00e1nky.<\/li>\n<li>Takisto uklad\u00e1me Cookie o tom, \u010di ste u\u017e dali s\u00fahlas s t\u00fdm, ako pou\u017e\u00edvame Cookies na na\u0161ej str\u00e1nke.\u00a0<\/li>\n<li>Na zapam\u00e4tanie u\u017e zobrazen\u00fdch oznamov, aby sme V\u00e1m ich opakovanie neukazovali dokola.\u00a0<\/li>\n<li>Pou\u017e\u00edvame aplik\u00e1cie tret\u00edch str\u00e1n ako Google Analytics, WordPress moduly, ktor\u00e9 ukladaj\u00fa Cookies aby mohli fungova\u0165 poriadne. Cookies n\u00e1m pom\u00e1haj\u00fa vylep\u0161i\u0165 sp\u00f4sob, ako sa V\u00e1m str\u00e1nka zobrazuje, napr\u00edklad v\u010faka n\u00edm nestrat\u00edte obsah ko\u0161\u00edka e-shopu, ak n\u00e1hodou zo str\u00e1nky omylom od\u00eddete.\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; custom_padding__hover=&#8221;|||&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3>Google Analytics<\/h3>\n<p>Pou\u017e\u00edvame Google Analytics softv\u00e9r na zber d\u00e1t ako pou\u017e\u00edvate na\u0161u str\u00e1nku. Rob\u00edme to na to aby sme mohli neust\u00e1le vylep\u0161ova\u0165 obsah a videli \u010do si na\u0161i n\u00e1v\u0161tevn\u00edci na str\u00e1nke pozeraj\u00fa.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>Google Analytics zber\u00e1 nasleduj\u00face \u00fadaje:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>str\u00e1nky, ktor\u00e9 nav\u0161t\u00edvite na na\u0161ej webovej str\u00e1nke<\/li>\n<li>ako dlho sa na str\u00e1nke zdr\u017e\u00edte<\/li>\n<li>ako ste sa na str\u00e1nku dostali<\/li>\n<li>na \u010do klik\u00e1te, ke\u010f si prehliadate str\u00e1nku<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Nezber\u00e1me Va\u0161e osobn\u00e9 \u00fadaje, meno ani adresu, preto tieto inform\u00e1cie nem\u00f4\u017eu by\u0165 zneu\u017eit\u00e9 na identifik\u00e1ciu Va\u0161ej osoby.<\/p>\n<p>Nepovo\u013eujeme Google zdie\u013eanie Va\u0161ich d\u00e1t.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Cookie<\/th>\n<th>Exspir\u00e1cia<\/th>\n<th>Popis<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>_ga<\/td>\n<td>2 roky<\/td>\n<td>Rozoznanie n\u00e1v\u0161tevn\u00edka.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>_gid<\/td>\n<td>24 hod\u00edn<\/td>\n<td>Rozoznanie n\u00e1v\u0161tevn\u00edka.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>_gat<\/td>\n<td>1 min\u00fata<\/td>\n<td>\n<p>Pou\u017e\u00edva sa na zmiernenie po\u017eiadaviek na server, ak je pou\u017eit\u00fd Google Tag Manager, tento cookie sa vol\u00e1\u00a0<code>_dc_gtm_&lt;property-id&gt;<\/code>.<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>_gac_&lt;property-id&gt;<\/td>\n<td>90 dn\u00ed<\/td>\n<td>\n<p>Obsahuje inform\u00e1cie t\u00fdkaj\u00face sa u\u017e\u00edvate\u013ea a kampan\u00ed. Ak je prepojen\u00fd Google Analytics s AdWords \u00fa\u010dtom, AdWords konverzia tagov na\u010d\u00edta tento cookie pokia\u013e neodvol\u00e1te s\u00fahlas\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/support.google.com\/google-ads\/answer\/7521212?hl=sk\">Viac inform\u00e1ci\u00ed.<\/a><\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>S\u00fahlas so sledovan\u00edm cez Google Analytics m\u00f4\u017eete odvola\u0165 nain\u0161talovan\u00edm si\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/tools.google.com\/dlpage\/gaoptout\" rel=\"external\">opt out of Google Analytics cookies<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; custom_padding__hover=&#8221;|||&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"document-title\">WordPress<\/h3>\n<p>Pri prihl\u00e1sen\u00ed, WordPress pou\u017e\u00edva\u00a0wordpress_[hash] cookie pre ukladanie prihlasovac\u00edch \u00fadajov, jeho pou\u017eitie je limitovan\u00e9 len pre administrat\u00edvne rozhranie. Po prihl\u00e1sen\u00ed,\u00a0WordPress nastav\u00ed wordpress_logged_in_[hash] cookie, ktor\u00fd informuje, \u010di ste prihl\u00e1sen\u00ed a kto ste.\u00a0WordPress takisto uklad\u00e1 nieko\u013eko few wp-settings-{time}-[UID] cookies. \u010c\u00edslo na konci je va\u0161e u\u017e\u00edvate\u013esk\u00e9 ID z datab\u00e1zy u\u017e\u00edvate\u013eov WordPress. Pou\u017e\u00edva sa na prisp\u00f4sobenie administrat\u00edvneho rozhrania.<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Cookie<\/th>\n<th>Exspir\u00e1cia<\/th>\n<th>Popis<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>wordpress_{HASH}<\/td>\n<td>2 t\u00fd\u017edne<\/td>\n<td>\n<p>Ukladanie prihlasovac\u00edch \u00fadajov, jeho pou\u017eitie je limitovan\u00e9 len pre administrat\u00edvne rozhranie, \/wp-admin\/<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>wordpress_logged_in_{HASH}<\/td>\n<td>2 t\u00fd\u017edne<\/td>\n<td>\n<p>Tento Cookie informuje, \u010di ste prihl\u00e1sen\u00ed a kto ste.<\/p>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>wordpress_settings-{TIME}-{UID}<\/td>\n<td>2 t\u00fd\u017edne<\/td>\n<td>WordPress takisto uklad\u00e1 nieko\u013eko few wp-settings-{time}-[UID] cookies. \u010c\u00edslo na konci je va\u0161e u\u017e\u00edvate\u013esk\u00e9 ID z datab\u00e1zy u\u017e\u00edvate\u013eov WordPress. Pou\u017e\u00edva sa na prisp\u00f4sobenie administrat\u00edvneho rozhrania.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2><span id=\"Commenters\" class=\"mw-headline\">Koment\u00e1re na blogu<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span class=\"mw-headline\">Ke\u010f n\u00e1v\u0161tevn\u00edk odo\u0161le koment\u00e1r k pr\u00edspevku na Va\u0161om blogu, zap\u00ed\u0161e sa mu Cookie na jeho po\u010d\u00edta\u010di. Ukladaj\u00fa sa inform\u00e1cie, ktor\u00e9 zad\u00e1 na Va\u0161om blogu o sebe, aby ich nemusel op\u00e4\u0165 ru\u010dne vypisova\u0165, ke\u010f sa vr\u00e1ti na V\u00e1\u0161 blog komentova\u0165 v bud\u00facnosti.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Cookie<\/th>\n<th>Exspir\u00e1cia<\/th>\n<th>Popis<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><tt>comment_author_{HASH}<\/tt><\/td>\n<td>1 rok<\/td>\n<td>Inform\u00e1cie o u\u017e\u00edvate\u013eovi, ktor\u00fd komentoval.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><tt>comment_author_email_{HASH}<\/tt><\/td>\n<td>1 rok<\/td>\n<td>Inform\u00e1cie o u\u017e\u00edvate\u013eovi, ktor\u00fd komentoval.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><tt>comment_author_url_{HASH}<\/tt><\/td>\n<td>1 rok<\/td>\n<td>Inform\u00e1cie o u\u017e\u00edvate\u013eovi, ktor\u00fd komentoval.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; custom_padding__hover=&#8221;|||&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3>Facebook Pixel<\/h3>\n<p>Facebook pon\u00faka viacero sp\u00f4sobov na kontrolu rekl\u00e1m zobrazen\u00fdch na z\u00e1klade aktiv\u00edt, ktor\u00e9 rob\u00edte na str\u00e1nke.<\/p>\n<p>Ak nechcete neha\u0165 Facebook pou\u017e\u00edva\u0165 tieto inform\u00e1cie na z\u00e1klade aktiv\u00edt na str\u00e1nke alebo aplik\u00e1ci\u00ed na Facebooku za \u00fa\u010delom zobrazenia relevantn\u00fdch rekl\u00e1m, m\u00f4\u017eete sa <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/settings\/?tab=ads\">odhl\u00e1si\u0165 tu<\/a>. Viac inform\u00e1ci\u00ed o online reklame zalo\u017eenej na z\u00e1ujmoch<a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/help\/164968693837950?helpref=faq_content\"> n\u00e1jdete tu<\/a>. Z\u00e1sady pou\u017e\u00edvania \u00fadajov od Facebooku <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/about\/privacy\/\">n\u00e1jdete tu<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Ak ste registrovan\u00fd Facebook u\u017e\u00edvate\u013e, nastavenia, ktor\u00e9 sprav\u00edte sa prejavia na v\u0161etk\u00fdch va\u0161ich zariadeniach. Ak nie ste registrovan\u00ed na Facebooku, mus\u00edte tieto nastavenia spravi\u0165 individu\u00e1lne pre ka\u017ed\u00fd prehliada\u010d.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>Z v\u00e1\u0161ho prehliada\u010da<\/p>\n<p>Spolo\u010dnos\u0165 Facebook dodr\u017eiava z\u00e1sady samoregul\u00e1cie pre online behavior\u00e1lnu reklamu a z\u00fa\u010dast\u0148uje sa programov na zru\u0161enie, ktor\u00e9 zaviedli <a href=\"http:\/\/www.aboutads.info\/choices\/\">Digital Advertising Alliance<\/a>, aliancia <a href=\"http:\/\/youradchoices.ca\/\">Digital Advertising Alliance v Kanade<\/a> a <a href=\"http:\/\/www.youronlinechoices.eu\/\">Eur\u00f3pska aliancia interakt\u00edvnej digit\u00e1lnej reklamy<\/a>. Z t\u00fdchto str\u00e1nok m\u00f4\u017eete odst\u00fapi\u0165 od v\u0161etk\u00fdch z\u00fa\u010dastnen\u00fdch spolo\u010dnost\u00ed.<\/p>\n<p>Z V\u00e1\u0161ho zariadenia<\/p>\n<p>Na Va\u0161om iPhone, iPade a Androide m\u00f4\u017eete zmeni\u0165 nastavenia t\u00fdkaj\u00face sa zobrazenia rekl\u00e1m na z\u00e1klade Va\u0161ich z\u00e1ujmov.<\/p>\n<p>Pre iPhone alebo iPad:<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>V nastaveniach<\/li>\n<li>Kliknite na S\u00fakromie<\/li>\n<li>Kliknite na Reklama<\/li>\n<li>Zapnite Limitovanie sledovania rekl\u00e1m<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>Pre Android (verzia 2.2 and viac) a Google Play Slu\u017eby (verzia 4.0 a viac):<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>V Google Nastavenia<\/li>\n<li>Reklama<\/li>\n<li>Dezaktivova\u0165 zobrazovanie z\u00e1ujmovo orientovan\u00fdch rekl\u00e1m<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Pravidl\u00e1 pou\u017e\u00edvania cookiesNa inrestsro.sk pou\u017e\u00edvame cookies pre zabezpe\u010denie \u010do najlep\u0161ieho z\u00e1\u017eitku na na\u0161ej webovej str\u00e1nke.Pod\u013ea legislat\u00edvy EU sme povinn\u00ed V\u00e1s informova\u0165 o pou\u017eit\u00ed t\u00fdchto Cookies na\u0161ou str\u00e1nkou a slu\u017ebami tret\u00edch str\u00e1n.\u010co je cookie?Cookie je mal\u00fd textov\u00fd s\u00fabor. Ke\u010f si prehliadate webov\u00fa str\u00e1nku, str\u00e1nka si uklad\u00e1 tento s\u00fabor do vyhraden\u00e9ho miesta pre Cookies na Va\u0161om po\u010d\u00edta\u010di [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_et_pb_use_builder":"on","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-2115","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.inrestsro.sk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/2115"